org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.robotplus.hardware

Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.robotplus.hardware.Robot

  • public class Robot
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing the entire robot for the season. It's set up so as to be modular and able to change things from outside of the class, but it's expected that teams will change this class every year to fit their robot better. It just works better.
    Since:
    4/10/17
